    "_srcBlendFactor": 770,
    "_dstBlendFactor": 771,
    "_string": "All symbols EXCEPT BONUS symbol pay left to right on each winning combination, \nwhen appearing on adjacent reels, starting with the leftmost reel.\n\nOnly highest win pays per line.\n\nEvery spin is played with one payline.\n\nPaytable presents wins for a bet equal to 1 coin and one winning payline. \nBet 10 will give you 10x the payout from the pay table.",
    "_N$string": "All symbols EXCEPT BONUS symbol pay left to right on each winning combination, \nwhen appearing on adjacent reels, starting with the leftmost reel.\n\nOnly highest win pays per line.\n\nEvery spin is played with one payline.\n\nPaytable presents wins for a bet equal to 1 coin and one winning payline. \nBet 10 will give you 10x the payout from the pay table.",
